    "Once a user selects a literature collection, the platform performs frequency statistics of words or n-grams within the selected collection.",
    "The output statistical results include a sorted frequency count and ratio.",
    "The frequency ratio is the ratio of the frequency count to the total number of characters in the selected collection.",
